{"title":"燕山，绿色的思念","authors":["周星辰"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":8,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕山，绿色的思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周星辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总有一种留恋在远山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总有一种情感在缠绵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几回回梦里军中行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几次次醒来梦难圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，燕山深处的军营——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我生命的绿色摇篮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告别了平原的故乡——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才感到崇山峻岭的壮观"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巡逻在崎岖的山道——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才懂得祖国边陲的遥远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警戒在风沙的哨所——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才知道战士肩负的重担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为丰腴的山川守卫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为富庶的祖国值班"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为繁华的都市站岗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为芬芳的泥土作战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用青春的富有——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装点生命的绿色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用青春的双手——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织和平的花篮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用青春的怒吼——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抵御狰狞的豺狼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用青春的热血——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谱写雄壮的诗篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，燕山——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我绿色的青春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我绿色的誓言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘不了亲筑的营垒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘不了熟悉的山川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门前还寒溪流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸边乍暖桃吐瓣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俯视近丛绿染枝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望远巅雪映天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊攀援阳坡上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云霭滞留峰峦间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在晨风中——拔正步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在晚霞里——练投弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱石滩上——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浸透着拓荒的汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山深处——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰鸣着施工的风钻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山洪呼啸——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驰骋着抢险的身影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合成演练——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弥漫着喷射的硝烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，燕山——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我绿色的人生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我绿色的营盘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常常怀恋军号的雄浑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常常追忆受阅的威严"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的步履"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春的英姿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的呐喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春的宣言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的雄风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春的骄傲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的辉煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春的灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘燕山——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给予我人生的光辉履历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给予我留下的追忆无限我愿在您指令的地点列队我愿按您确定的战略——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国的和平统一而战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，燕山——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我绿色的风采"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我绿色的思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：辽宁辽阳市人大常委办公室）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}